videos.description: After a turnover,  Eastern Kentucky's Jormaru Brown drives to the cup, but Tennessee's Grant Williams is there and denies the shot.
videos.headline: Williams rejects Brown attempt

videos.description: Off an inbounds pass from Lamonte Turner, Tennessee's Kyle Alexander cuts, goes up and throws down a nasty one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Alexander gets air and hammers it down

videos.description: After an Eastern Kentucky steal, Tennessee's Yves Pons goes straight up for the two-handed block on Nick Mayo.
videos.headline: Pons goes vertical and denies Mayo

videos.description: Off the missed free throw, Tennessee gets the rebound and Yves Pons sprints down courts, jumps and crushes the rim on a nice alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Pons runs the court, flies and destroys the rim

videos.description: Yves Pons sprints down court, jumps and crushes the rim on a nice ally-oop dunk and off a steal, Jordan Bowden throws down an emphatic one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Back-to back dunks puts Tennessee up 17

videos.description: Tennessee's Kyle Alexander misses, fights for the rebound and rocks the rim plus the foul.
videos.headline: Alexander hustles and slams it down

videos.description: Tennessee's Yves Pons goes up and throws down a emphatic alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Pons rocks alley-oop dunk
